<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id79293a4c-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s689f"><num value="689f">§ 689f.</num><heading> Fees</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Except as provided in <ref href="/us/usc/t15/s689e/d">section 689e(d) of this title</ref>, the Administrator may charge such fees as it deems appropriate with respect to any guarantee or grant issued under this part.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id79293a4d-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/pl/85/699/tIII/s357">Pub. L. 85–699, title III, § 357</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/106/554/s1/a/8/s1/b/3">Pub. L. 106–554, § 1(a)(8) [§ 1(b)(3)]</ref>, <date date="2000-12-21">Dec. 21, 2000</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/114/2763">114 Stat. 2763</ref>, 2763A–660.)</sourceCredit>
